    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me over the years. It's perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that still looks great pulling into the driveway. I've taken care of the maintenance, so it's ready to hit the road for its next big adventure! Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
